quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  13,19,Kodi iye amene adziwa chimene chavumbulutsidwa kwaiwekuchokerakwaAmbuyewakokutindichoonadindi olingana ndi iye amene ali wakhungu? Ndi okhawo amene ali ndinzeruameneazindikira
  13,20,Iwoameneamakwaniritsa lonjezo la Mulungu ndipo saphwanya lonjezolo
  13,21,"Iwo amene amalumikiza chimene Iye wawalamula kuti chikhale chimodzi, amaopa Ambuye wawo ndipo amaopa zoopsa zimene zidzaoneka patsiku lachiweruzo"
  13,22,"Ndi iwo amene amapirira chifukwa chofuna mtendere wa Mulungu modzipereka, amapitiriza mapemphero awo ndi kupereka zimene tawapatsa mseri kapena moonekera, ndipo amaletsa choipa pochita chinthu chabwino. Awa ndiwo amene adzaone zinthu zokoma"
  13,23,"Iwo adzalowa ku Paradiso kwa muyaya pamodzi ndi ena a makolo awo angwiro, ndi akazi awo ndi ana awo. Kuchokera ku khomo lililonse angelo adzadza nati kwa iwo"
  13,24,“Mtendere ukhale pa inu chifukwa cha kupirira kwanu pa mavuto ochuluka. Yodalitsika ndi mphotho ya ku Paradiso!”
  13,25,"Iwoameneamaphwanyalonjezola Mulunguatalilandira ndipo amalekanitsa zinthu zimene Iye adawalamulira kuti azilumikize, ndipo amachita zinthu zoipa pa dziko lapansi, temberero lidzaikidwa pa iwo ndipo malo awo okhala adzakhala osasangalatsa"
  13,26,Mulungu amapereka mowolowa manja kwa aliyense amene Iye wamufuna ndi monyalapsa ndipo iwo amasangalala m’moyo uno pamene chisangalalo cha m’moyo uno ndi cha kanthawi kochepa kwambiri pofanizira ndi cha moyo umene uli nkudza
  13,27,"Ndipo iwo amene sakhulupirira amati, “Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani chizindikiro sichidaperekedwe kuchokera kwa Ambuye wake?” Nena, “Ndithudi Mulungu amasocheretsa aliyense amene wamufuna ndipo amatsogolera onse amene amalapa kwa Iye.”"
  13,28,Iwo ndi amene amakhulupirira ndipo mitima yawo imapeza mpumulo akamakumbukira Mulungu. Ndithudi m’chikumbukiro cha Mulungu mitima imapeza mpumulo